
==========================
   CREDITS
==========================

The development and maintenance of the WanT code is promoted by: 

  * S3 Center, Istituto Nanoscienze, 
    of the Italian CNR (http://www.nano.cnr.it) 

  * the University of North Texas
    (http://ermes.unt.edu) 

The present release of the WanT package has been realized
by Andrea Ferretti (CNR-NANO), Luis A. Agapito (UNT), 
   Arrigo Calzolari (CNR-NANO), Marco Buongiorno Nardelli, (UNT), Aug 2013.


