=========================================================================
Original contributions
=========================================================================

The routines for the calculation of the maximally-localized Wannier functions 
were originally written by: 

- Nicola Marzari and David Vanderbilt (1997); 
- Ivo Souza, Nicola Marzari and David Vanderbilt (2002); 


The routines for the calculation of the quantum conductance were 
originally written by:

- Marco Buongiorno Nardelli (1998); 
- Arrigo Calzolari, Nicola Marzari, and Marco Buongiorno Nardelli (2003).


The iotk library is written and maintained by Giovanni Bussi (2002).


